OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FA legal challenge against one of
OL,7,FBritain's biggest supermarkets that
OL,8,Fhas rumbled on for 10 years finally
OL,9,Freaches court today, as more than
OL,10,F60,000 Asda workers accuse the company
OL,11,Fof sex discrimination.
OL,13,FThe case against Asda, which claims
OL,14,Fthat the jobs of mainly women working
OL,15,Fon the shop floor are unfairly
OL,16,Funderpaid compared to predominantly
OL,17,Fmale warehouse workers, could have
OL,18,Fhuge implications for the entire
OL,19,Fretail sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
