OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FThe GMB union claimed that if Asda
OL,7,Floses the equal pay case, the
OL,8,Fsupermarket giant could be looking at
OL,9,Fhistoric payments worth #1.2bn as well
OL,10,Fas an increased annual pay bill of
OL,11,F#400m.
OL,13,FIt comes after an email leaked to ITV
OL,14,FNews revealed that an independent
OL,15,Fexpert, who was commissioned by the
OL,16,Fcourt to compare the store workers'
OL,17,Fjobs to those in the distribution
OL,18,Fcentres, had concluded that the
OL,19,Fwomen's roles were of equal value.
