OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FThe findings, revealed in an email
OL,7,Fsent by lawyers Leigh Day to tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of claimants, appeared to be
OL,9,Fa major boost for the shop floor
OL,10,Fworkers.
OL,12,FThe case is being heard at the
OL,13,FManchester Employment Tribunal, with
OL,14,Farguments being made by Asda and the
OL,15,Fclaimants until November 22. A
OL,16,Fdecision is likely to be made in
OL,17,FJanuary.
