OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FIt comes after the retailer Next lost
OL,7,Fa similar case, where 3,540 workers
OL,8,Faccused it of paying shop workers less
OL,9,Fthan distribution workers.
OL,11,FAlthough the tribunal did not find
OL,12,Fdirect discrimination, it judged that
OL,13,Fthe company had failed to show that
OL,14,Flower pay rates were not the result of
OL,15,Fgender-based discrimination.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
