OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FNadine Houghton, GMB National Officer,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Asda workers had had to fight
OL,8,Ffor ten years, with bosses fighting
OL,9,Fthem every step of the way, just to
OL,10,Fget to today's hearing. They will not
OL,11,Fgive up now."
OL,13,FShe argued that "the entire retail
OL,14,Fsector has been built on the
OL,15,Fstructural undervaluing of women's
OL,16,Fwork".
