OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FShe said that if the court finds the
OL,7,Fjobs are of equal value then Asda's
OL,8,Fmajority owners - TDR Capital - should
OL,9,Fget around the table for settlement
OL,10,Ftalks.
OL,12,F"The new owners have loaded billions
OL,13,Fof pounds of debt onto ASDA's balance
OL,14,Fsheet - yet last year they reported a
OL,15,Fpre-tax profit of #180m," Houghton
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"TDR Capital was founded by now
OL,19,Fbillionaire, Manjit Dale - there is
OL,20,Fenough money to pay these women what
OL,21,Fthey are owed."
