OL,3,CDecade-long sex discrimination legal
OL,4,Cchallenge against Asda reaches court
OL,6,FSusan Brierly, 69, left her home in
OL,7,FOldham early this morning to be at the
OL,8,Fcourt.
OL,10,FShe worked at Asda for 46 years and
OL,11,Fhas been a claimant for some years.
OL,13,F"It's been a long time waiting, it
OL,14,Fcould've been resolved," she said, as
OL,15,Fshe got ready to head out.
OL,17,F"Every time we go to court they just
OL,18,Fappeal so it drags on years and years.
OL,19,FHow long do we have to wait? People
OL,20,Fare dying (while they wait for the
OL,21,Foutcome)."
