OL,6,FShop floor jobs include checkout
OL,7,Foperators, customer service workers
OL,8,Fand those unloading products and
OL,9,Fbringing them into the stores.
OL,11,FAn Asda spokesperson said: "We fully
OL,12,Frespect the right of current and
OL,13,Fformer colleagues to bring this case,
OL,14,Fhowever, we strongly reject any claim
OL,15,Fthat Asda's pay rates are influenced
OL,16,Fby gender. There are numerous
OL,17,Fdifferent jobs within retail and
OL,18,Fwithin warehouses.
