OL,6,F"We continue to defend these claims
OL,7,Fbecause retail and distribution are
OL,8,Ftwo different industry sectors that
OL,9,Fhave their own distinct skill sets and
OL,10,Fpay structures."
OL,12,FThe company has pointed out that there
OL,13,Fare men who work on the shop floor and
OL,14,Fwomen in the warehouses.
OL,16,FIn fact, around 30% of claimants are
OL,17,Fmale but the case is based on equal
OL,18,Fpay claims because the shop floor
OL,19,Fworkforce is predominantly female and
OL,20,Fthe warehouses are predominantly male.
