OL,6,FThe lawyers will argue that Asda has
OL,7,Fundervalued the skills on the shop
OL,8,Ffloor, in comparison to more physical
OL,9,Fskills, but Asda workers have also
OL,10,Ftold ITV News that they unload the
OL,11,Fproducts and so are carrying out
OL,12,Fphysical work similar to in the
OL,13,Fdistribution centres.
OL,15,FJackie Sloan, from near Poole, told
OL,16,FITV News last year, that equal pay
OL,17,Flaws came into play in 1975, when she
OL,18,Fwas 15.
